name: CELL
tagline: CELL, an audio-visual game built in Cinder and SuperCollider
body:
### Welcome to CELL's GitHub Page.
CELL is an open-source Audiovisual experience built in [Cinder](http://libcinder.org/) and the [SuperCollider](http://supercollider.sourceforge.net/) programming language

![L](http://amputek.github.com/Cellv0/images/cell-splashscreen.png)
